# Data caches (downloaded FDA datasets, regenerable)
# NDC auto-downloads at startup (~244MB), so it stays out of git. DECRS/DSCSA/
# Orange Book require a manual, interactive export (FDA blocks scripted
# requests for these) and are only ~16MB total -- small enough, and otherwise
# unobtainable on a fresh deploy, so those are committed. See
# data/MANUAL_DOWNLOADS.md.
data/raw/*
!data/raw/decrs/
!data/raw/decrs/**
!data/raw/dscsa/
!data/raw/dscsa/**
!data/raw/orange_book/
!data/raw/orange_book/**
data/cache/

# OS
.DS_Store

# AI coding tool config (local dev only)
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
